Output e2e/tests/artifacts/hello-sync.ascii
Output e2e/local/hello-sync.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 18
Set Width 1200
Set Height 600
Set TypingSpeed 0ms

Hide
Type "export PS1='$ '"
Enter
Sleep 50ms

Type "clear"
Enter
Sleep 50ms

Type "cd $E2E_TEST_REPO"
Enter
Sleep 50ms

Type "clear"
Enter
Sleep 50ms
Show

Type "verti sync"
Enter
Sleep 100ms
